  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Soak the<strong> rice noodles</strong> in <strong>cold water</strong> and set them aside to soften&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Peel and&nbsp;halve the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Slice half <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>onion</strong>, and grate the other half <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/775.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/775.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/775.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/775.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/775.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pork mince</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>and&nbsp;<strong>grated onion</strong>&nbsp;to a large bowl and crumble in 1/2&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span>&nbsp;<strong>chicken stock cube</strong></p>\r\n<p>Knead thoroughly with clean hands for 2-3 min or until fully combined, then shape&nbsp;into 10 <span class=\"text-danger\">[20]<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><strong>meatballs</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/775.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/775.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/775.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/775.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/775.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> meatballs</strong> and<strong> sliced red onion</strong> and cook for 3 min, turning occasionally, until the <strong>meatballs</strong> are browned all over&nbsp;</p>",
